Privacy Statement &nbsp; This privacy policy will explain how mrinrt.org uses personal data we collect from you when you use our website. &nbsp;
How do we collect your data? You directly provide mrinrt.org with the data we collect. We collect data and process data only when you complete the questionnaire regarding your intention to participate in the MRinRT Symposium 2025. &nbsp;
How will we use your data? mrinrt.org collects your data so that we can collect applications for the participation in the planned event.
